For example, if you study the word DOG, a rating of 0 indicates that you would not remember DOG at test, while a rating of 100 indicates full certainty that you would remember the word DOG at test.
When making your ratings, it is criticial that you use the full range of the scale. You will be disqualified for only giving ratings of 0 or 100!
